# Commands used in this section

$ docker build -f Dockerfile .
$ docker run <image id>
$ docker-compose down && docker-compose up --build

# How to select multiple words in visual code 
# select the words before the set of key word that you want to copy together
# Press the command button many times to select the same block multiple times.
# Press the arrow right to put the cursor the correct point
# Press Option + shift + right arrow to select all key words that you want to copy in the text
# Command + C
# Command + V


